Legislation that would <EVENT eid="e13" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="NONE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="would">ban</EVENT> 19 semi-automatic weapons is <TIMEX3 tid="t7" type="DATE">currently</TIMEX3> being  <EVENT eid="e14" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESENT" aspect="PROGRESSIVE" polarity="POS" modality="none">worked</EVENT> out in Congress.&#13;
The Justice Department figures are based on the results of household  interviews nationwide with the victims.&#13;
